	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default<span id=notbold>[2.25]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>I would like to say that this, although it might be too heavy, is a new weapon for druids. Although all of you people that hate druids do so, you should really think that druids dont have much of an advantage in anything. And although this wep might be too heavy for most druids my druid has 91 str when buffed, and he is only lvl 20(self-buffed) So the weight shouldn't be a problem, and also, If you are a druid who wishes to use 1hs instead of 1hb, which is a good choice, since the epic is a 1hs, Druids are always on the lookout for a better 1hs weapon. Everytime they see that druids can use a sword they think WOW! no matter how terrible the weapon is. With this new sword, this should keep the druids alive at least a bit longer against fire casting casters. Also, it allows for the druids, once out of mana and thinks it is appropriate, to make some slashing fun at whatever the group is killing. Additionally, this would help when kiting and you ran out of mana. Even if you got the enemy down to like 100hp, most druids would not be able to bring that baddie down manaless. I would like to say that this weapon is a great addition to the druid arsenal and i would request to learn where to get it. <br><br>20 druid,<br>Morell Thule<br>&nbsp;<br>The flames can die, but I never will, MWAHAHA</td></tr>
